01:50:56.631 --> 01:50:59.304
- We just found out Haldeman's the fifth.
- I'm not your source on that.

01:50:59.391 --> 01:51:02.110
We're not asking you to be our source.
All we're asking is to confirm it.

01:51:02.191 --> 01:51:03.306
I'm not your source on Haldeman.

01:51:03.391 --> 01:51:05.347
Okay, look, when you were
questioned by the Grand Jury...

01:51:05.431 --> 01:51:06.466
You had to name names.

01:51:06.551 --> 01:51:09.987
<i>- Of course, everything they asked, yes.
- Lf they asked you. All right if they...</i>

01:51:12.671 --> 01:51:15.185
<i>I don't know... Say we wrote a
story that said that Haldeman...</i>

01:51:15.271 --> 01:51:16.989
was the fifth name to control the fund.

01:51:17.071 --> 01:51:20.063
- Would we be in any trouble?
- Would we be wrong?

01:51:23.431 --> 01:51:25.262
Let me put it this way.

01:51:25.591 --> 01:51:28.663
I would have no problems if
you wrote a story like that.

01:51:28.751 --> 01:51:30.343
- You wouldn't?
- No.

01:51:32.111 --> 01:51:34.022
- That's okay. Yeah.
- Okay.

01:51:34.511 --> 01:51:36.706
- Oh, you had a baby.
- Yes, my wife did.

01:51:36.791 --> 01:51:38.110
- Little boy or girl?
- That's terrific.

01:51:38.191 --> 01:51:39.226
It's a girl.

01:51:39.311 --> 01:51:40.983
- Congratulations.
- Thank you.

01:51:41.071 --> 01:51:42.789
- We're sorry to bother you.
- Yeah.

01:51:42.871 --> 01:51:45.465
- Will you give our best to her?
- I will.

01:51:48.431 --> 01:51:51.662
Well, I think that, Woodward,
and I am curious of the fact...

01:51:51.751 --> 01:51:54.629
<i>that the FBI, in its entire
inquiry, never talked to the...</i>

01:51:54.711 --> 01:51:57.828
Or did any inquiries into the second
most-powerful man to the President.

01:51:57.911 --> 01:51:59.469
<i>You don't seem to understand.</i>

01:51:59.551 --> 01:52:02.019
<i>No, you get nothing
about Haldeman out of me.</i>

01:52:02.311 --> 01:52:04.063
But we don't need to know anything, Joe.

01:52:04.151 --> 01:52:06.221
Tomorrow we're going
with a story on the FBI.

01:52:06.311 --> 01:52:07.346
<i>Now, what does that mean?</i>

01:52:07.431 --> 01:52:09.308
And we're going to
establish in that story...

01:52:09.391 --> 01:52:11.700
that you guys just about
blew the whole investigation.

01:52:11.791 --> 01:52:13.509
<i>Oh, no, we didn't miss so much.</i>

01:52:13.591 --> 01:52:15.502
You didn't know Haldeman had
control of the slush fund?

01:52:15.591 --> 01:52:17.263
<i>Oh, yes, we did. It's all in our files.</i>

01:52:17.351 --> 01:52:19.581
<i>- Not about Haldeman.
