01:52:24.871 --> 01:52:27.305
That's the confirmation right there.

01:52:28.431 --> 01:52:30.786
Wait a minute, wait a
sec. Did he say John?

01:52:31.311 --> 01:52:33.347
- He said Haldeman.
- He said John Haldeman.

01:52:33.431 --> 01:52:35.820
What the hell difference does it
make if he said Isaiah or David?

01:52:35.911 --> 01:52:36.980
There's only one Haldeman.

01:52:37.071 --> 01:52:40.381
Yeah, well, Isaiah or David
aren't assistants to the President.

01:52:40.871 --> 01:52:42.668
I don't know, it still feels thin.

01:52:42.751 --> 01:52:44.707
Christ, I just wish we
knew if we could print this.

01:52:44.791 --> 01:52:46.827
Now wait a minute, we didn't
make them do these things...

01:52:46.911 --> 01:52:48.310
but once they did, they're fair game!

01:52:48.391 --> 01:52:50.586
Harry, let's go over your
sources again. I want to hear it.

01:52:50.671 --> 01:52:53.663
Sloan told the Grand Jury. He
answered everything they asked him.

01:52:53.751 --> 01:52:55.582
That means there's gotta
be a record somewhere.

01:52:55.671 --> 01:52:58.663
He told the Grand Jury, the FBI
confirms. What more do you need?

01:52:58.751 --> 01:52:59.866
I happen to love this country.

01:52:59.951 --> 01:53:02.021
You know, we're not a bunch
of zanies out to bring it down!

01:53:02.111 --> 01:53:03.749
Harry, weren't you
arguing the opposite way?

01:53:03.831 --> 01:53:05.310
No, not at all.

01:53:05.471 --> 01:53:06.506
All right, now hold it.

01:53:06.591 --> 01:53:08.661
One thing has nothing
to do with the other.

01:53:08.871 --> 01:53:11.180
We're about to accuse Haldeman
who only happens to be...

01:53:11.271 --> 01:53:13.102
the second-most-important
man in this country...

01:53:13.191 --> 01:53:15.864
of conducting a criminal conspiracy
from inside the White House.

01:53:15.951 --> 01:53:17.623
It would be nice if we were right.

01:53:17.711 --> 01:53:19.588
- Have you double-checked
your sources? - Jesus.

01:53:19.671 --> 01:53:22.344
- Bernstein, are you sure on this story?
- Absolutely!

01:53:22.431 --> 01:53:24.103
- Woodward?
- I'm sure.

01:53:24.671 --> 01:53:26.946
I'm not. It still seems thin.

01:53:27.231 --> 01:53:28.505
Get another source.

01:53:28.591 --> 01:53:31.583
How many fucking sources
do they think we've got?

01:53:34.871 --> 01:53:38.147
- Are you sure Deep Throat won't confirm?
- He won't confirm, I told you that.

01:53:38.231 --> 01:53:39.425
What about the guy in Justice?

01:53:39.511 --> 01:53:41.422
