Hi, I finally got Sloan on the phone.

02:05:35.111 --> 02:05:36.988
Why the hell didn't you
tell me over the phone?

02:05:37.071 --> 02:05:39.107
- Woodward says phones aren't safe.
- Can't trust them.

02:05:39.191 --> 02:05:40.909
- Come on in.
- We can't come in, sir.

02:05:40.991 --> 02:05:43.903
Woodward says there's
electronic surveillance.

02:05:59.911 --> 02:06:01.981
- Surveillance? Who's doing it?
- It's being done.

02:06:02.071 --> 02:06:04.301
People's lives are in
danger. Maybe even ours.

02:06:04.391 --> 02:06:06.109
What happened to that
Justice source of yours?

02:06:06.191 --> 02:06:07.943
I guess I made the
instructions too complicated.

02:06:08.031 --> 02:06:10.306
Because he thought I said "hang up"
when I just said "hang on".

02:06:10.391 --> 02:06:12.302
- Oh, Jesus!
- The story is right.

02:06:12.391 --> 02:06:14.302
Haldeman was the fifth
name to control that fund...

02:06:14.391 --> 02:06:17.349
- and Sloan would've told the Grand Jury.
- Sloan wanted to tell the Jury.

02:06:17.431 --> 02:06:18.784
- Why didn't he?
- Because nobody asked.

02:06:18.871 --> 02:06:20.270
Nobody asked him.

02:06:20.351 --> 02:06:22.103
The cover-up had little
to do with the break-in.

02:06:22.191 --> 02:06:24.625
It was to protect covert operations
and the covert activities...

02:06:24.711 --> 02:06:26.986
involving the entire U.S.
Intelligence community.

02:06:27.071 --> 02:06:29.585
Did Deep Throat say that
people's lives are in danger?

02:06:29.671 --> 02:06:30.706
Yes.

02:06:30.791 --> 02:06:34.340
- What else did he say?
- He said everyone is involved.

02:06:42.031 --> 02:06:44.591
You know the results of
the latest Gallup Poll?

02:06:44.671 --> 02:06:47.390
Half the country never even
heard of the word "Watergate".

02:06:47.471 --> 02:06:49.189
Nobody gives a shit.

02:06:51.711 --> 02:06:54.066
You guys are probably
pretty tired, right?

02:06:54.471 --> 02:06:56.701
You should be. Go on home.

02:06:57.271 --> 02:06:59.990
Get a nice hot bath,
rest up 15 minutes...

02:07:00.391 --> 02:07:02.700
then get your asses back in gear.

02:07:03.151 --> 02:07:06.826
We're under a lot of pressure,
you know, and you put us there.

02:07:08.151 --> 02:07:12.508
Nothing's riding on this except the
First Amendment of the Constitution...

02:07:12.591 --> 02:07:16.061
freedom of the press, and
maybe the future of the country.

02:07:18.031 --> 02:07:20.226
Not that any of that matters...

02:07:20.431 --> 02:07:23.582
but if you guys fuck up
again, I'm going to get mad.

02:07:25.551 --> 02:07:26.825
Goodnight.

02:07:53.591 --> 02:07:55.627
<i>And now, fellow Americans...</i>

02:07:55.911 --> 02:07:59.745
<i>the Honorable Chief Justice will
administer the oath of office...</i>

02:08:00.311 --> 02:08:03.348
<i>to the President of the
United States of America.</i>

02:08:03.431 --> 02:08:05.023
<i>Mr. Chief Justice.</i>

02:08:26.351 --> 02:08:29.980
<i>Mr. President, are you ready
to take the constitutional oath?</i>

02:08:30.191 --> 02:08:34.309
<i>If you will place your left hand on
the Bible and raise your right hand...</i>

02:08:34.391 --> 02:08:38.987
<i>and please repeat after me. "I,
Richard Nixon, do solemnly swear...</i>

02:08:39.111 --> 02:08:41.625
<i>"I, Richard Nixon, do solemnly swear...</i>

02:08:41.711 --> 02:08:46.068
<i>"...that I will faithfully execute the office
of President of the United States...</i>

02:08:46.311 --> 02:08:49.940
<i>"...that I will faithfully execute the office
of President of the United States...</i>

02:08:50.031 --> 02:08:54.468
<i>- "...and will, to the best of my ability...
- "...and will, to the best of my ability...</i>

02:08:54.551 --> 02:08:58.749
<i>"...preserve, protect and defend
the Constitution of the United States...</i>

02:08:58.951 --> 02:09:02.785
